      • newTag

        public NBTBaseTag<T> newTag()
        Create a fresh tag of this type. For list and compound tags the tag can be safely cast to an NBTListTag or NBTCompoundTag or equivalently with a NBTBaseTag.get() call.
        Ex: 
             NBTCompoundTag tag = NBTType.COMPOUND.newTag().get();
        Returns:
        the newly created tag
